    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Simlarni Ulash Rejimi</h2>
        <p>● RJ25 bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>NSW Smart Servo Moduli RJ25 porti orqali ulanishi mumkin. Makeblock Orion-da RJ25 portidan foydalanganda, uni mos keluvchi portga ulashingiz kerak:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_smartservo_rj25.jpg" alt="NSW Smart Servo RJ25 Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">

        <p>● Dupont simi bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>Dupont simidan modulni Arduino UNO asos paneliga ulash uchun foydalanilganda, uning Signal pinini PWM pinga, RX va TX pinlarini Arduino RX va TX pinlariga quyidagicha ulash lozim:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_smartservo_dupont.jpg" alt="NSW Smart Servo Dupont Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Dasturlash Bo'yicha Qo'llanma</h2>
        <p>Arduino Dasturlash</p>
        <p>Agar dastur yozish uchun Arduino dan foydalansangiz, NSW Smart Servo Modulini boshqarish uchun quyidagi koddan foydalanishingiz mumkin:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-cpp">
// Arduino dastur kodi
#include &lt;Servo.h>

Servo smartServo;
const int servoPin = 9;

void setup() {
    smartServo.attach(servoPin);
    Serial.begin(9600);
}

void loop() {
    for (int pos = 0; pos &lt;= 270; pos += 1) {
        smartServo.write(pos);
        delay(15);
    }
    for (int pos = 270; pos >= 0; pos -= 1) {
        smartServo.write(pos);
        delay(15);
    }
}
        </code></pre>
